lead_paragraph: Soren Kjeldsen and Thorbjorn Olesen remained on course to claim a first World Cup of Golf for Denmark after shooting a two-under-par 70 in Saturday's foursomes to extend their overnight lead to four strokes.

headline.print_headline: Dominant Danes Extend World Cup Lead in Melbourne
